  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n                        \u003cp\u003eLocated within a suburb of Mumbai, India, the \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/DCidQe6onQi/?img_index=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eVaulted Monochrome Haus\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e, designed by \u003ca href=\"https://www.digarch.net/home\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDIG Architects\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e, merges a monochromatic color palette with minimalist aesthetics and cozy elegance. The 4,300-square-foot residence is designed for a family of four – comprising a finance entrepreneur, a Ph.D. scholar, and their two adult children pursuing studies abroad – masterfully balancing social functionality with personal comfort.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=566002\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-566002\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-2-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Modern living room with minimalist design, featuring grey sofas, a circular coffee table, spherical decor items, and a round pendant light. Walls are adorned with abstract art.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-2-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-2-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-2-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-2-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-2.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHaving collaborated with the clients on previous projects, DIG Architects entered the design process with an established rapport and mutual understanding. This trust empowered the architects to push creative boundaries, drawing inspiration from structural forms. The vaulted ceiling became the project’s defining feature, harmonizing architectural intent with aesthetic purity. Complementing this central theme, materials such as gabion walls, frosted glass bricks, and Ceppo De Gre stone were integrated to evoke a cohesive yet strikingly unique environment.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=566003\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-566003\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-3-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Modern living room with grey sofas, large windows, and a potted plant. Black decorative items sit on low tables, and curtains are partially drawn. Minimalist design with natural light.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-3-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-3-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-3-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-3-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-3.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=566004\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-566004\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-4-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A spacious, modern living room with gray sofas, a round coffee table, and large windows with sheer curtains, offering a view of greenery outside.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-4-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-4-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-4-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-4.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe apartment’s layout, while largely retaining its original structure, underwent strategic adjustments to enhance spatial efficiency. A guest bedroom was repurposed into a study, allowing for an expanded primary suite with a spacious walk-in closet. The living area, envisioned as a central social hub, connects to auxiliary spaces like a custom-designed bar and an open kitchen, emphasizing inclusivity and interaction.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=566005\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-566005\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-5-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Modern interior with dark furniture, a textured bar with stools, hanging glasses, and a grid-patterned wall.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-5-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-5-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-5-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-5-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-5.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFrom the entrance, visitors are greeted by an interplay of light and texture. A frosted glass brick partition, which diffuses light into soft, ambient glows, separates the entrance from the bar. The living room, a voluminous rectangular space, features a subdivided vaulted ceiling that adds depth and character. This area serves as the heart of the home, accommodating relaxed gatherings, dining, and even film screenings with ease.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=566006\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-566006\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-6-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A modern bar area with a green wall backsplash, shelves with bottles, a stone-filled bar counter, and four hanging lights.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-6-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-6-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-6-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-6-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-6.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=566007\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-566007\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-7-810x1216.jpg\" alt=\"Modern interior with a sculpted bust on a black console table, flanked by a textured wall. High chairs and a patterned art piece complete the space.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1216\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-7-810x1216.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-7-800x1201.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-7-768x1153.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-7-1023x1536.jpg 1023w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-7.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=566008\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-566008\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-8-810x456.jpg\" alt=\"Modern living and dining area with gray couches, a rectangular dining table, dark gray chairs, and a large spherical pendant light. Large windows and greenery are visible outside.\" width=\"810\" height=\"456\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-8-810x456.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-8-800x450.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-8-768x432.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-8-600x337.jpg 600w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-8.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAdjacent to the living space, the dining area is intentionally designed to foster social connections, with sightlines encouraging interaction. Overhead, the Moon lighting pendant by Davide Groppi becomes a centerpiece, adding an ethereal quality to the room.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=566009\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-566009\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-9-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Modern dining room with a long table, six gray chairs, and a large, spherical light fixture. Curtains cover the windows, and a textured wall with a vase completes the minimalist design.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-9-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-9-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-9-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-9.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=566010\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-566010\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-10-810x1211.jpg\" alt=\"Modern hallway with sleek design, polished marble floor, and a large black circular wall art. A red chair is visible at the end of the hall, near a bright window.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1211\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-10-810x1211.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-10-800x1196.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-10-768x1148.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-10-1027x1536.jpg 1027w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-10.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTrue to its name, the Vaulted Monochrome Haus employs a grayscale palette, accented by Ceppo De Gre marble – a rugged stone rarely used in Indian interiors. This monochromatic scheme is brought to life with strategic pops of greenery, which introduce vitality and warmth into the space. Every detail, from the sandwiched metal mesh in the cabinetry to the oak veneer in the study, reflects an intentional minimalism that prioritizes functionality without compromising elegance.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=566011\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-566011\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-11-810x639.jpg\" alt=\"Modern bedroom with a four-poster bed, neutral bedding, a round bedside table, wall-mounted lights, and a large window with sheer curtains.\" width=\"810\" height=\"639\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-11-810x639.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-11-800x631.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-11-768x605.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-11.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=566012\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-566012\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-12-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Modern bedroom with a black four-poster bed, matching side table, gray linens, a stylish black chair, wall-mounted lamps, and a gray-textured floor.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-12-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-12-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-12-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-12-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-12.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe private quarters carry forward the overarching theme while embracing individual identities. The primary bedroom exudes sophistication with its four-poster bed framed by a backlit installation of frosted glass bricks. Sliding partitions offer versatile configurations, blending functionality with design ingenuity. Meanwhile, the daughter’s room, a departure from the gray-dominated aesthetic, features a predominantly white palette, embodying brightness and softness.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=566013\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-566013\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-13-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Luxurious marble bathroom with a large bathtub, a sink, and a well-lit mirror. The walls and floor are covered in grey marble tiles. A window grid provides ambient light.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-13-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-13-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-13-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-13-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-13.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=566014\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-566014\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-14-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Minimalist bedroom with a large bed, gray textured wall, a potted plant, and a window with a view of a rocky landscape.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-14-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-14-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-14-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-14.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=566015\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-566015\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-15-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Modern bedroom with a gray marble accent wall, light gray upholstered bed, striped bedding, and a sleek black nightstand with a round lamp.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-15-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-15-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-15-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-15-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-15.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTransforming conceptual elements like vaults into tangible forms posed significant challenges. The ceilings required bespoke templates for precision, while integrated lighting demanded innovative solutions to maintain the purity of design. Similarly, creating sliding wall systems to address spatial conflicts in the primary bedroom showcased the architects’ problem-solving prowess.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=566016\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-566016\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-16-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A modern bedroom with a minimalist design, featuring a bed, gray chair at a small green desk, abstract wall art, and a green armchair against textured walls and flooring.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-16-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-16-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-16-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-16.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=566017\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-566017\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-17-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"Modern living room with a green cushioned chair, black corner floor lamp, abstract geometric artwork on the wall, and a sleek black horizontal-paneled wall.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-17-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-17-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-17-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-17-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-17.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=566018\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-566018\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-18-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Luxurious bathroom with grey marble walls and floors, a glass shower enclosure, a white bathtub, and a modern sink area with a round mirror.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-18-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-18-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-18-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-18-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-18.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=566019\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-566019\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-19-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Bathroom with gray marble walls and countertop, a large mirror, a wall-mounted faucet, and two spherical pendant lights. A recessed shelf with books is visible in the reflection.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-19-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-19-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-19-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-19-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Vaulted-Monochrome-Haus-Mumbai-DIG-Architects-19.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFor more on DIG Architects, visit \u003ca href=\"https://www.digarch.net/home\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003edigarch.net\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003ePhotography by \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/ishifishy/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003eIshita Sitwala\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n                        \n                                                    \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson-100x100.jpg\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson.jpg 2x\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" alt=\"\"/\u003e                                    \u003c/p\u003e\n                                \u003c/div\u003e\n\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003eCaroline Williamson is Editor-in-Chief of Design Milk. She has a BFA in photography from SCAD and can usually be found searching for vintage wares, doing New York Times crossword puzzles in pen, or reworking playlists on Spotify.\u003c/p\u003e\n                                    \n                                \u003c/div\u003e\n                            \u003c/div\u003e\n                                            \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
